Description:
  The fetty:setup generator will add / install the necessary gems 
  to your Gemfile and configure the gems.
  
  this will installed :
	- cancan
	- simple_form
	- kaminari
	- jquery-rails
	- carrierwave
	- ckeditor
	- meta_search

  optional gem :
	- mongoid
	- devise
	- thinking_sphinx
	
Examples:
    rails g fetty:setup
		* will install the default gems
	rails g fetty:setup --mongoid --devise
		* will include to instal mongoid and devise
	rails g fetty:setup --skip-meta-search --thinking-sphinx
		* will skip meta_search installation and install thinking_sphinx